            <h5 class="mt-4 font-weight-bold">Elevate Customer Engagement</h5>
            <p>Personalize the shopping experience with tailored recommendations, manage customer accounts, and build lasting relationships with your readers.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-5">
        <p class="font-italic">"Our Bookstore Management System provides everything you need to succeed, whether you're managing a small local shop or a large franchise."</p>
        <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg mt-3" href="/Books/Index">Explore Our Features</a>
